high_descs: Turn around and go to the top cabinet, to the right of the window, across from you.
Pull out the sponge from the cabinet.
Turn to your left and go to the end of the counter, then turn to the pan on the counter, to your right.
Place the sponge in the fry pan on the counter.
Pick up the fry pan with the sponge inside it.
Turn to your right and go to the sink right next to you.
Place the pan with the sponge inside it in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan containing a sponge, in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and step forward to the kitchen counter.  Look up to the kitchen cabinet.
Open the cabinet and remove the sponge in front of the dispenser, then close the door.
Come down to the floor, turn left and walk to the intersection and turn right  to face a pan.
Place the sponge upright on the left side of the pan.
Pick up the pan from the kitchen counter.
Turn right and walk forward till you reach the kitchen sink on the left.  Turn and face the sink.
Place the pan with the sponge in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take a sponge out of the cabinet to put in a pan and place in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the counter right of the sink.
Pick up the sponge in the cabinet above the counter, right of the sink.
Bring the sponge to the pan on the counter, left of the sink.
Put the sponge in the pan on the counter.
Pick up the pan with sponge on the counter.
Bring the pan to the sink on the right.
Put the pan with sponge in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with sponge in it, in the sink.
